Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A melancholy Monday has arrived.}Thứ 2 khốn khổ lại đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.45,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Feels good to be over your cold, huh?}Thật may khi chị khoẻ lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.48,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:21.20,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Or are you happy your cold \Nlet you miss school a few days?}Hay là chị vui vì được nghỉ học mấy ngày?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.84,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:24.07,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{How come?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.41,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{You always say you wanna stay home...}Chị lúc nào cũng nói muốn ở nhà mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I don't like going to school,}Chị không thích đến trường,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.12,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{but for someone like me, \Neven one day of failing to attend class}nhưng với những kẻ như chị, dù chỉ nghỉ 1 ngày...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:34.68,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{puts me in risk of being \Nforgotten by my classmates.}cũng sẽ khiến mọi người quên mất đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:38.19,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Guess you're a real pain \Nin your own ass, Sis!}Chị đúng là con nhỏ phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.77,Default,Futari,0,0,0,,{Oh, and Mom says it's time to eat!}A, mẹ nói đến giờ cơm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yes, it's true.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:48.76,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I could burst from the sheer volume \Nof nuisance I inflict upon myself.}Chị cũng tự biết bản thân mình phiền phức mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But wait a minute.}Cơ mà khoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I joined a band, and I'm \Nworking part-time at a club!}Mình tham gia ban nhạc, làm bán thời gian ở Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:00.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Perhaps I've graduated from my introversion!}Vậy là không còn là người hướng nội nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:02.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll take my guitar to school again.}Mang ghita đến trường nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:07.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Someone's bound to talk to me this time!}Và lần này nhất định sẽ có ai đó bắt chuyện!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:15.63,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yep. Putting the onus on \Nothers fails once again.}Đúng rồi, làm gì có chuyện đó chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.10,DefaultTop,Classmate B,0,0,0,,{Hey, did you watch the latest Oto-Station?}Nè cậu xem show diễn ở trường quay Oto chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.63,DefaultTop,Classmate A,0,0,0,,{I did did!}Rồi rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.50,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,{You can stream BAKWIMPS again!}Nghe nói có thể xem lại đó, BAKWIMPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.62,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,{I've been listening to them\Nso much since yesterday,}Hôm qua tớ nghe nhiều quá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.55,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,{they're still playing in my head!}nên giờ cứ dính trong đầu hoài nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:24.52,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,{Uh-oh!}Ừm ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Band talk!}Tán nhảm về ban nhạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.49,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,{What's up, Gotoh-san?}Có chuyện gì vậy Gotou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:32.48,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,{You hardly ever talk to anyone!}Hiếm khi mới thấy nói to đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{All my preparation assumed \Nothers would approach me first,}Mình chuẩn bị cho mọi cuộc đối thoại khi được bắt chuyện,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:37.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{so I don't know how \Nto start a conversation...}nên không biết cách bắt chuyện trước...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.64,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I forgot.}Tớ quên mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.05,Default,Classmates A & B,0,0,0,,{In that short a time?!}Chưa gì đã quên sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:42.29,Default,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,{It's lunchtime!}Đến giờ ăn trưa rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{This is for the best.}Vậy là tốt nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:51.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{If I'd managed to talk to them, \Nright about now...}Nếu mình nói chuyện đàng hoàng với họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.72,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,{Barging into our convo like that...}Tự nhiên cậu lại bắt chuyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.19,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,{Was she listening in the \Nwhole time or something?!}Vậy là nghe lén từ nãy hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:59.93,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,{I didn't know she was such a creep!}Không ngờ cậu lại là người như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.33,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's definitely how it'd be!}Chắc chắn là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll never rise above my station again.}Thôi, từ bỏ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll live under the radar forever!}Mình sẽ chìm xuống đáy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.39,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Thank you for the meal.}Cảm ơn vì bữa ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:15.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Still... A quiet place like this \Nis just perfect for lunch.}Cơ mà... một nơi yên bình để ăn trưa nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm glad I found a nice spot.}Thật may khi tìm thấy nơi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.14,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's awkward eating all alone\Nin the classroom.}Ăn trưa một mình trong lớp khó xử lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:24.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And once I become a popular guitarist, \NI'll go on Oto-Station and say...}Và đến khi mình trở thành tay ghita nổi tiếng,\N mình sẽ đến trường quay Oto và nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.12,Default,Guitar Man,0,0,0,,{What were you like in high school?}Hồi trung học bạn làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.34,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I didn't have any friends back then.}Hồi đó tôi không có bạn bè.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:36.55,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I often ate lunch in a dark corner \Nfilled with desks and janitorial supplies.}Nên hay ăn trưa trong một góc nhỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:41.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can awe people with how much \NI've changed! Y'know how it is...}Mình sẽ khiến mọi người há hốc mồm... Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.43,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,{Karaoke was so much fun the other day!}Hôm bữa đi karaoke vui nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:43.43,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{People!}Có người!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.93,DefaultTop,Girl Student B,0,0,0,,{Kita-chan's such a great singer.}Kita-chan hát hay ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.03,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,{I heard she played guitar in a band before she quit.}Nghe nói cậu ấy từng chơi ghita trước khi nghỉ đó.
