Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.92,DefaultTop,Girl Student B,0,0,0,,{Wow! Now that's musical talent!}Giỏi ghê vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.14,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Band?}Ban nhạc?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Nijika nói muốn tìm một tay ghita biết hát nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Since my cold kept me from \Nworking for a few days,}Do bị cảm nên mình nghỉ bữa giờ.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I must find a guitar-slash-vocalist \Nto prove my commitment to Kessoku Band!}Phải chứng minh sự hữu dụng vói ban nhạc!
