Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But the thought of going up \Nto a total stranger...}Nhưng bắt chuyện với người lạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.79,Default,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.33,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Heya!}Chào!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.53,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,{I'm super sorry, but I have \Na huge favor to ask...}Xin lỗi nhé, nhưng tớ có chuyện muốn nhờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What kind of girl is she?}Cậu ấy là người như nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.88,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.84,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,{Would you mind pitching in at \Nour basketball game next week?}Tuần tới cậu thay tớ tham gia trận bóng rổ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She's pretty!}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.33,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{Hey, sure thing!}Ừm, được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,280)}{She's super nice!}Quá dễ thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:23.93,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H1A1F1C&\fnComic Sans MS\3c&HFBFFFD&\b0\pos(317.725,319.692)}{Kids, don't try this at home!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.65,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll land a three-pointer!}Có khi tớ ném 3 điểm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:23.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,280)}{She's pretty, and athletic, and popular,}Xinh đẹp, giỏi thể thao và nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.93,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0,0,0,,{Awesome! Thanks!}Tuyệt quá! Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{\i0}{and}{\i1}{ she plays the guitar...}Và chơi ghita...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:29.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm supposed to issue an \Ninvitation to someone like }{\i0}{her}{\i1}{?!}Sao mình có thể mời một người như vậy chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{In fact, my identity...}Cơ mà điểm nổi bật của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{My entire identity is crumbling!}Sẽ bị phá huỷ mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.15,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(695,1)\fnArial Black\fs32\an8\c&H8065E5&\3c&HE2CEE8&\bord3\pos(451.413,17.393)}{Identity}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.73,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Pwip.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.99,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{What was that sound?}Âm thanh gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.43,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.80,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.18,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.93,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.57,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked being soaked by the rain,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.94,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{because my face looked better clouded over}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.58,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be afraid of the storm}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.41,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{while waiting for the sky to burst}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:26.37,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum through the light's distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:30.79,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to make thunder roar}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:36.59,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum beyond the pain}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:40.72,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control}
