Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.40,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Here's your cola!}Cola đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.10,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Um, so the senpai you \Nwanted to get closer to...}Đàn chị mà cậu muốn gần gũi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:25.96,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.44,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It's Ryo-senpai.}Là chị Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.47,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Here ya go.}Xin mời.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.93,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Unlike you, I have very impure motives.}Không như cậu, động cơ của tớ có hơi mờ ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.36,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I saw Senpai playing on the street,}Một lần tớ thấy chị ấy diễn trên phố.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.99,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{and fell head-over-heels for her.}Và đã đổ mất luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Ryo-san was in another band, too?}Chị Ryo từng ở ban nhạc khác à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.51,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Her above-it-all attitude, her unisex look...}Phong cách lạnh lùng, vẻ ngoài ngầu lòi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.62,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It all makes me squee!}Tất cả đều khiến tớ nghẹt thở.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Nghẹt thở?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.38,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{And she just looks so }{\i1}{right}{\i0}{ \Nholding an instrument!}Và chị ấy trông thật ngầu khi cầm nhạc cụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.24,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, I know what you mean!}A, tớ hiểu ý của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.76,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-When I hold mine, it looks more \Nlike the instrument's holding me.}K-Khi tớ cầm nhạc cụ cứ như nó đang ôm lấy tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.09,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Right? You end up like\Nan appendage to the instrument.}Phải đó. Cậu cứ như một phần phụ của nhạc cụ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.22,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{I wonder how that happens?}Tớ không biết cảm giác đó thế nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's like we're best \Nbuddies all of a sudden...}Kiểu như mình với cậu ấy là đôi bạn thân vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.51,DefaultTop,Kita,0,0,0,,{That's one thing about Ryo-senpai that—}Còn nữa nhé, chị Ryo ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.64,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{Um, can I get a cassis orange?}Xin lỗi, một nước cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.53,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Right! Coming right up!}Vâng! Có ngay ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye, buddies! \NI'll know my place next time...}Tạm biệt bạn thân! Tớ có hơi quá trớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.52,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{After I heard her play,}Sau khi xem chị ấy diễn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.37,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I followed Ryo-san's activities for a while,}tớ đã theo dõi một thời gian,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.68,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{and she dropped out of her \Nlast band pretty suddenly.}và tự nhiên chị ấy rời ban nhạc cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.82,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Huh...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.92,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Then I found out she was \Nrecruiting for Kessoku Band,}Sau đó thì chị ấy tham gia ban Kessoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.75,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{and without thinking, I said I'd do it.}tớ không nghĩ gì hết xin vào luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Such initiative! Extroversion abounds!}H-Hướng ngoại cao quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.96,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{A band is like your second family, you know?}Vì ban nhạc như gia đình thứ 2 mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.01,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Family?}Gia đình?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:41.37,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you spend more time with them \Nthan with your actual family,}Ừm, cậu càng bên cạnh họ thì\N họ sẽ dần trở thành gia đình mình,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.14,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{and you're all chasing the same dream...}và mọi người cùng nhau theo đuổi giấc mơ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.88,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It's a mysterious relationship, \Ncloser than friends or significant others.}Nó là mối quan hệ bí ẩn, trên tình bạn và tình yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.52,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I've never done clubs or anything similar,}Hồi xưa tớ chưa từng tham gia CLB hay ban nhạc,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.72,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{so I've always wanted to be part of that.}thế nên tớ rất ngưỡng mộ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I get you.}Hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I always wanted it too...}Mình cũng luôn muốn thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:16:00.08,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Yes... I wanted to join Kessoku Band \Nand become Senpai's girl!}Phải... tớ muốn tham gia ban nhạc\N và trở thành cô gái của chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.84,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{So much deeper and more \Nintimate than friendship!}Sâu hơn tình bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wait. Is Kita-san kind of not-okay?}Ủa? Kita-chan khá là nguy hiểm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.28,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But that's all the more reason}Nhưng chính vì thế,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.70,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I can't join the band now.}hiện tại tớ không thể tham gia ban nhạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.57,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I flaked out once already. \NI'm too irresponsible.}Tớ đã bỏ chạy một lần, một con người vô trách nhiệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.45,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I don't deserve to be in the band.}Tớ không xứng đáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:34.38,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H3D583C&\pos(320,198.5)}{Tickets go on sale at }{\c&H25726A&}{5 pm}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.53,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Okay, good work, all. Feel free to head home.}Mọi người vất vả rồi. Hôm nay nghỉ đi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.46,Default,Nijika Ryo & Kita,0,0,0,,Mọi người vất vả rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:34.38,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,Vất vả rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.28,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Thanks for everything today.}Hôm nay cảm ơn vì mọi chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.84,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Good luck with your band!}Chúc may mắn với ban nhạc mới nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.56,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'll keep rooting for you!}Tớ sẽ cỗ vũ cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.89,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Goodbye!}Tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Hey...}K-Khoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.82,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bocchi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.72,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Are you all right, Gotoh-san?}Cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.93,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You're not still worried about me, are you?}Cậu vẫn lo cho tớ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.80,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:11.98,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Like I said before, \NI can't join Kessoku Band.}Tớ không thể tham gia ban nhạc đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.80,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,Không chơi được ghita lại còn bỏ trốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.31,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I... I... I...}Tớ... tớ... tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.39,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I also ran away before the concert.}Tớ cũng từng bỏ chạy trước buổi diễn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.02,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I hid in a trash can, and...}Trốn vào thùng rác... và...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.72,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A-A-And also...}V-Và cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.40,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let's get you up, Bocchi-chan.}Chị nâng em lên nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.69,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{One, two...}Hai, ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.69,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Here we go!}Lên nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.32,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{K-Kita-san, your left hand...}K-Kita, tay trái của cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.96,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-You had calluses on your fingertips.}T-Tay trái của cậu có những vết chai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.78,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I... I th-think...}T-Tớ nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.64,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{You'd have to be practicing \Nthe guitar pretty hard for that.}Em đã luyện tập ghita rất nhiều nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.66,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah!}P-Phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:50.42,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Kita-chan, we'd love to have you \Nrocking out with us in Kessoku Band!}Kita-chan, chị cũng muốn em tham gia ban nhạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.13,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Why would you let me...}Tại sao lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.92,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Because if you hadn't flaked out, \Nwe'd never have met Bocchi-chan!}Vì nếu em không bỏ chạy thì chị đã \Nkhông gặp được Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:58.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah!}P-phải đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I've always wanted to have a band,}Chị luôn muốn tạo một ban nhạc,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:10.34,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{so I get how it feels intimidating \Nand aspirational at the same time.}thế nên chị hiểu được cảm giác sợ hãi và lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.90,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-So do I!}T-Tớ cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.49,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry. That came out \Nlouder than I expected.}X-Xin lỗi, em nói hơi to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You'd be happy to have her too, right, Ryo?}Cậu cũng vui vì em ấy quay lại mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.59,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I'll only have to pay one-quarter \Nof the studio and quota fees.}Tớ sẽ chỉ phải trả 1/4 tiền thuê phòng thu âm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.99,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Be a little less honest, would you?}Thẳng thắn đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.56,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I can be part of Senpai's quota!}Mình có thể trở thành một phần của chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.38,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{So much for that healthy \Nmoving-on thing, I guess...}Hình như mọi chuyện diễn ra nhanh quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.06,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But I still can't play the guitar...}Nhưng em vẫn không thể chơi ghita...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.88,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That's okay!}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.81,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan will teach you!}Bocchi sẽ dạy em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.72,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Eh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.00,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah.}Ừm ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.99,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Ehh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.02,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You will?}Thật à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:43.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes!}À ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can't exactly turn her down now!}Không thể từ chối...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.90,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.24,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'll work really hard to \Nplay guitar in Kessoku Band!}Tớ sẽ cố hết sức để chơi được ghita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:07.48,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Oh, but you should probably give up \Nthat party lifestyle of yours...}Cơ mà mọi người nên từ bỏ lối sống thác loạn đó đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.46,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You're dancing like mad\Nevery night, right?}Đêm nào mấy chị cũng quẩy hết nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.96,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Where'd you hear that?!}Em nghe từ đâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm glad it's all mended.}Thật may khi mọi chuyện đã suôn sẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:18.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It came out like a mess, but I'm glad \NI stopped Kita-san from leaving.}Lúc đầu như một mớ rắc rối,\N nhưng thật may khi Kita không rời đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I worked really hard!}Mình đã cố hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.78,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Well, I gotta head out now...}V-Vậy em xin phép...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.73,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, don't go!}Khoan đã Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.98,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You're today's MVP!}Hôm nay em là MVP mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.36,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{You're the reason we're back together.}Nhờ em mà ban nhạc hồi sinh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.86,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Gotoh-san!}Cảm ơn cậu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:44.78,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\q2\c&H070F0E&\3c&HE8F3F0&\bord1.5\clip(147,0,640,80.19)\move(-2000,35,0,35)}{Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.28,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Gosh, well, it was nothing, \Nreally, honestly...}E-Em có làm gì đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.62,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It obviously wasn't nothing for you.}Hành động em đang ngược lại đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.78,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-san wears her heart on her sleeve.}Em dễ hiểu thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:49.47,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But I practiced for so long, and yet \NI never really learned how to play guitar.}Nhưng tớ luyện tập nhiều lắm mà vẫn không chơi được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.98,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It just made this quiet 'bum-bum' sound.}Âm thanh nó cứ bùm bùm thế nào ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-You're sure it wasn't a bass?}C-Cái đó là bass mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.45,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Hey, I'm not }{\i1}{that}{\i0}{ ignorant!}Tớ không ngốc đến nỗi thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:58.85,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{A bass has four strings, right?}Bass có 4 dây mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.76,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{See? It's got the full six strings!}Nè, có 6 dây còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.79,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Some do have six strings...}V-Vài loại có 6 dây...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.31,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{That's a six-string bass.}Đây là bass 6 dây.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.03,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{K-Kita-san!}K-Kita?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.57,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It cost me two years' \Nadvance allowance from my dad,}Nó tốn 2 năm tiền tiêu vặt của tớ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.48,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{not to mention my New Year's money...}và thêm cả tiền mừng tuổi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.15,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:33.05,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And so, Kessoku Band officially \Nhad all their members.}Và thế là ban Kessoku đã có đủ thành viên.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.50,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{No more!}Không chịu đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:40.17,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I hereby quit the guitar!}Tớ sẽ bỏ ghita.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What? Are we breaking up already?}Hả? Chưa gì đã từ bỏ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.44,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Is this one defective too?}Nè, nó bị lỗi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.64,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Did I get another bass?}Lại bass hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.51,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-No, that's definitely a guitar...}K-Không, nó là ghita...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:52.32,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry I whine so much.}Tớ xin lỗi vì đã than vãn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:56.09,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I know you're giving up your time after \Nclass and during lunch to teach me...}Tớ biết cậu đã hi sinh giờ ăn trưa để dạy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.44,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Hey, it's not...}À không hẳn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:03.24,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{With Ryo-senpai lending me this guitar, \Nand everyone helping... I have to do my best.}Chị Ryo cho tớ mượn cả ghita,\N mọi người đang cố gắng giúp đỡ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:09.07,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But I really am glad... that Ryo-san \Nb-bought that bass off of you...}N-Nhưng mà thật may khi\N chị Ryo mua lại đàn cho cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:09.87,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.58,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But when she gave me the money...}Nhưng khi chị ấy đưa tớ tiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:18.04,Flashback,Ryo,0,0,0,,{This is the last of my money, \Nso I'll be eating weeds from now on.}Đây là số tiền cuối cùng của chị,\N từ giờ phải ăn cỏ sống qua ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.43,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{That was a joke, right?}Đó là đùa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.88,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She might have been serious!}Có vẻ là thật đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.41,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Oh, come on...}Lại nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.09,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{This one's so hard to hold.}Nó khó quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.45,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{The F chord is too hard!}Hợp âm F khó quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That takes me back.}Hoài niệm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I was this way at the start, too.}Mình cũng từng như thế nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:56.83,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Ryo-senpai! Hello...}Chào chị Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.77,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{You guys're here early.}Mấy đứa đến sớm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Sh-She really is eating weeds!}C-Chị ấy ăn cỏ thật kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.38,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Senpai's so wild!}Chị thật hoang dã!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:19.80,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{The tune that plays when my loneliness \Nand the pedal are stepped on}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:25.35,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Tracks down my cheeks over and over again}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:29.01,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{The pounding of my loneliness}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.11,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Is joined by the rhythm of the snare drum}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.20,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{To create a solid pulse}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.73,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Someone, please remove \Nthe distortion on my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.70,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{And take a look inside me}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:45.71,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Nobody can get inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:49.21,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{But it's the kind of night \Nwhen I hope someone will}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:51.71,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Distortion it's Motion}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:55.14,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Once it starts, there's no stopping it}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:59.36,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Limits can be overwritten with experience}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.70,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.76,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Distortion is always like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:07.22,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{My heart takes off, outpacing my left brain}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:08.86,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Toward where you are}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.49,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{An escort to the next note}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.21,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Distortion on my day-to-day anguish}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.05,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{The chord I play when I'm alone at night}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:18.51,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Is it the same for you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:21.13,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{I spent all those days chasing my ideal image}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:25.27,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{Play an F chord with distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:29.31,Songs_ED,ED,0,0,0,,{So loud that the needle swings off the scale}
